snippet.title: Occulto Demo trailer
snippet.description:
Kickstarter campaign:  https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1117146839/occulto?ref=azz66g

Occulto is an indie adventure game with a focus on artistic hand - drawn pictures and a non verbal game play. We have a demo on the stores, we are developing the whole game.

Game demo here: https://onelink.to/occulto
